ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectOrder No. 170 - (Saskatchewan) Provincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 170 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the federal government to provide financial assistance to the province of SASKATCHEWAN with respect to the RAINSTORM causing damage south of Montreal Lake from September 5 to 7, 2010.
